<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The healing gained from killing a jungle creature has been reduced to 2.5% of its maximum Health, down from 5%.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 1 (June 06, 2013)</h4><I>Dev Notes - An additional effect has been added to the Hunter role to address late game utility concerns for this role.</I><ul><li>Choosing the Hunter Role will now also grant a 25% chance to gain 20 bonus vim when killing a jungle creature. This is in addition to the already existing bonuses provided by the Role.</li></ul>